@PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health

### Get Top Scores
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores?count=10&gameMode=Default

### Save High Score
POST {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerInitials": "TST",
  "score": 1500,
  "gameMode": "Default"
}

### Check if High Score
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores/check/1500?gameMode=Default

### Get Player Rank
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores/rank/1500?gameMode=Default

### Test Connection
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores/test

### Diagnostics
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/highscores/diagnostics

### Get Player Stats
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stats/TST

### Get All Stats
GET {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stats

### Record Game Session
POST {{PoBabyTouchGc.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stats/record
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "initials": "TST",
  "score": 1500,
  "circlesTapped": 75,
  "playtimeSeconds": 180
}
